<div class="post-title">
	<h2><a href="https://www.thaipbsworld.com/thai-court-rejects-bail-request-again-for-ratsadon-leader-parit-penguin-chiwarak/">Thai court rejects bail request again for Ratsadon leader Parit “Penguin” Chiwarak </a></h2>
	<ul class="post-tags">
		<li><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>April 19, 2021</li>
		<li><i class="fa fa-user"></i>by <a href="https://www.thaipbsworld.com/author/kitipat-t-cgmail-com/" title="Posts by Kitipat Chuensukjit" rel="author">Kitipat Chuensukjit</a></li>
		<li> <span class="comm">Comments Off<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Thai court rejects bail request again for Ratsadon leader Parit “Penguin” Chiwarak</span></span></li>
	</ul>
</div>
<div class="post-content">
	<p>The Criminal Court rejected another bail application for anti-establishment Ratsadon leader Parit “Penguin” Chiwarak today (Monday), on the grounds that there is no reason to change the previous bail decisions,&#8230;</p>
