	<h2><a href="https://www.thaipbsworld.com/sanam-luang-access-closed-with-cargo-containers-to-block-protesters/">Sanam Luang access closed with cargo containers to block protesters </a></h2>
	<ul class="post-tags">
		<li><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>March 20, 2021</li>
		<li><i class="fa fa-user"></i>by <a href="https://www.thaipbsworld.com/author/nadbunnaggmail-com/" title="Posts by Nad Bunnag" rel="author">Nad Bunnag</a></li>
