<div class="post-content">
	<p>Police have blocked access to Sanam Luang with cargo containers and razor-wire to prevent ReDem Restart Democracy (ReDem) protesters, a youth wing of the anti-establishment Ratsadon group, from entering the&#8230;</p>
	<a href="https://www.thaipbsworld.com/sanam-luang-access-closed-with-cargo-containers-to-block-protesters/" class="read-more-button"><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-right"></i>Read More</a>
